Task 1 1. Move file from untracked to commit and the whole way back. Note: Do not skip any stage.

git checkout master
touch Homework2.txt 
git add .
git commit Homework2.txt 
git status 
git log 
git reset --soft HEAD~1
git restore --staged Homework2.txt

